These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, action, martial-arts, spy
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, bus, train, trike
1. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
3. the person driving the bus is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person driving the train##1
5. the person driving the trike is between the person driving the bus and the person driving the train##2
6. the person watching spy movies is the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | scientific     | martial-arts | action |
| Transport     | scooter     | train | trike  | bus      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, metal, d&b, funk
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, tram, boat, airplane
1. the fan of metal is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
2. the person driving the airplane is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of funk is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
4. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
5. the fan of d&b is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the train is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | classical | metal    | funk     | d&b  |
| Transport     | train    | boat | tram | airplane |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, electronic, soul, ambient
4 different pets are kept: mouse, guinea-pig, chinchilla, horse
1. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
2. the fan of electronic is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
4. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the fan of soul##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | electronic   | soul   | dubstep  | ambient |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | horse | chinchilla | mouse  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, rock-climbing, woodworking, drawing
There are 4 different nationalities: german, colombian, italian, malaysian
1. the malaysian is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person who's hobby is writing and the italian##2
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3
4. the italian is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
5. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
6. the german is on the right of the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | writing | drawing | woodworking  |
| Nationality   | colombian  | german   | malaysian  | italian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, lemonade, juice, cola
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, video-games, board-games, gardening
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | mirinda    | lemonade   | juice | cola    |
| Hobby      | video-games | chess | board-games       | gardening |

