.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, sprite, almond-milk, water
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, skateboard, subway, car
1. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person driving the subway is between the person driving the car and the person drinking almond-milk##2
3. the person driving the motorbike is between the person driving the subway and the person drinking tea##2
4. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | tea | almond-milk | water | sprite |
| Transport   | skateboard | motorbike  | subway    | car  |

