.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-7::.
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, japanese, german, indonesian
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, bus, quad-bike, scooter
1. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the polish##1
2. the polish is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
4. the german is between the japanese and the indonesian##2
5. the person driving the bus is the person driving the bus##1
6. the person driving the bus is between the person driving the quad-bike and the indonesian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Nationality   | polish | indonesian | german | japanese     |
| Transport     | bike | scooter  | bus   | quad-bike |

