.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, photography, writing, chess
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, comedy, musical, fantasy
1. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person who's hobby is chess is the person watching comedy movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
6. the person watching comedy movies is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Hobby         | chess | writing | magic-tricks | photography   |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | musical | spy      | fantasy |

