.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-9::.
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, goldfish, goat, mouse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, cycling, climbing, skateboarding
1. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the owner of the mouse##1
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left or far right##3
6. the owner of the goldfish is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person who's sport is cricket##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Pet     | guinea-pig | goldfish   | goat      | mouse      |
| Sport   | cycling     | climbing | cricket | skateboarding |

