.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, blues, hip-hop, techno
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, canadian, british, indonesian
1. the dutch is on the right of the canadian##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is between the indonesian and the canadian##2
3. the fan of blues is the canadian##1
4. the british is on the left of the canadian##1
5. the fan of techno is on the left or right of the dutch##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | blues | hip-hop      | techno   |
| Nationality   | british  | canadian    | dutch | indonesian |

