.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, singing, skydiving, drawing
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, van, car, trike
1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person driving the van##1
3. the person driving the trike is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
5. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
6. the person driving the car is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby       | rock-climbing | skydiving | drawing    | singing      |
| Transport   | car       | trike       | van | quad-bike |

