.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, thai, spanish, egyptian
4 different pets are kept: dog, mouse, hedgehog, lizard
1. the thai is on the far right##1
2. the colombian is the colombian##1
3. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
4. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the thai##3
5. the spanish is on the left or right of the egyptian##3
6. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the egyptian##3
7. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | colombian | spanish  | egyptian | thai |
| Pet           | hedgehog     | lizard | dog    | mouse     |

