.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-14::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, watermelon, papaya, cranberry
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, teacher, coach, engineer
1. the person eating cranberry is on the left or right of the teacher##3
2. the teacher is on the right of the coach##1
3. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the accountant##1
4. the teacher is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating papaya is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Food   | watermelon  | apple | cranberry  | papaya      |
| Job    | engineer | accountant | coach | teacher |

