.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, reading, baking, sudoku
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, jazz, disco, folk
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1
2. the fan of jazz is on the left of the fan of disco##1
3. the person who's hobby is reading is the fan of folk##1
4. the fan of jazz is the person who's hobby is baking##1
5. the fan of disco is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
6. the fan of disco is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
7. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | reading | sudoku | baking | board-games |
| Music-Genre   | folk     | soul       | jazz   | disco      |

