.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-19::.
There 4 different types of food: zucchini, broccoli, cranberry, carrot
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, librarian, firefighter, fisherman
1. the person eating carrot is on the left of the firefighter##1
2. the fisherman is on the left or right of the firefighter##3
3. the librarian is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
4. the firefighter is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
5. the firefighter is on the left of the librarian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1        |      2       |   3    |   4    |
| Food   | carrot        | zucchini       | cranberry   | broccoli |
| Job    | fisherman | firefighter | librarian | lawyer  |

